OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSteve Lamacq to end daily  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBBC Radio 6 Music show     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC Radio 6 Music DJ Steve Lamacq is to
OL,6, scale back his afternoon shows from    
OL,7, five days a week to one, saying he's "a
OL,8, bit knackered" after 18 years.         
OL,10,FLamacq has hosted the station's daily  
OL,11,Fweekday teatime show since 2005.       
OL,13,FHe will take a break in October before 
OL,14,Freturning with a weekly show on Mondays
OL,15,Fin January. Huw Stephens will take over
OL,16,Fhis slot from Tuesdays to Fridays.     
OL,18,FLamacq said "the obsessive way I do    
OL,19,Fthis job hasn't really left enough     
OL,20,Ftime" for his wife and young daughter. 
